node.text:
Getting you close to nature in some of the wildest and most remote places on Earth is what @lindbladexp do best. Whether it’s manning the spotting scopes all night to ensure a polar bear sighting or orchestrating a landing at a wildlife site to coincide with sunrise, their expedition teams create thrilling moments for you!

Check out @LindbladExp for wildlife moments and tag #whereiexplore to share your exploration photos with us. 

#LindbladPartner #EarthFocus
Photos by:
1. Michael S. Nolan
2. @richreidphoto
3. @jcalvofoto
5: @colbyoutdoors

node.text:
Breathtaking Canada 🇨🇦 From stunning mountain landscapes, to unique cities and some of the prettiest lakes you’ll ever see, Canada really has it all!

Photos by @mthiessen

Locations:
1-3. Niagara Falls, Ontario
4. Spirit Island, Alberta
5. Jasper, Alberta
6. Golden fields near Stony Plain, Alberta
7. Emerald Lake, British Columbia
8. Moraine Lake Road, Alberta
9. Lake Louise, Alberta
10. Edmonton, Alberta

Explore. Share. Inspire: #earthfocus
